@prefix : <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-datastruct#> .
@prefix bs: <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core#> .
@prefix xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-datastruct>
  a owl:Ontology ;
  owl:imports <https://bytestar.org/ontology/bytestar-core> ;
  rdfs:label "ByteStar Data Structures & ABIs" ;
  rdfs:comment "MPHF/LOUDS/XOR table contracts, cache alignment, ABI versioning." .

### Core data structures
:MPHFTable a owl:Class .
:LOUDSTrie a owl:Class .
:XORFilter a owl:Class .
:Bitset a owl:Class .

### ABI contracts
:abiVersion a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain rdfs:Resource ; rdfs:range xsd:string .
:byteLayout a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain rdfs:Resource ; rdfs:range xsd:string .
:cacheAligned a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain rdfs:Resource ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Table specifications
:lookupComplexity a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :MPHFTable ; rdfs:range xsd:string .
:constantTime a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :MPHFTable ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:perfectHashing a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain :MPHFTable ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### Memory layout guarantees
:l1Cacheable a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain rdfs:Resource ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:fixedSize a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain rdfs:Resource ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .
:noMallocOnHotPath a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain rdfs:Resource ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .

### ByteCore interface compliance
:implementsABI a owl:ObjectProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:Subsystem ; rdfs:range rdfs:Resource .
:abiCompliant a owl:DatatypeProperty ; rdfs:domain bs:Subsystem ; rdfs:range xsd:boolean .